<HEADLINE>
<P>
HOLIDAY CLOSINGS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Today is Presidents' Day. The following schedule will be in effect: 
</P>
<P>
 * City, county and federal offices will be closed.Westminster city offices 
will remain open, however. 
</P>
<P>
 * County, state and federal courthouses will be closed. 
</P>
<P>
 * City and county libraries will be closed.  
</P>
<P>
 * Banks and savings and loans will be closed. 
</P>
<P>
 * Schools, colleges and universities will be closed. Chapman University will 
be open. 
</P>
<P>
 * Mail: There will be no postal service. 
</P>
<P>
 * Trash: Will be collected on its regular schedule. 
</P>
<P>
 * Buses: OCTA buses and special service transit will run on regular schedule.  
</P>
<P>
 * Parks: All city- and county-run parks will be open during regular hours. 
</P>
