<DOCNO> LA022194-0145 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 015905 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
February 21, 1994, Monday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 5; Column 1; National Desk 
</P>
