<HEADLINE>
<P>
LIFETIME'S 'OUR HOME' TO PREMIERE JUNE 6 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 ABC has its "Home" show, and soon Lifetime will have "Our Home," a similarly 
styled program with tips on cooking, interior decorating and fashion. 
</P>
<P>
 For the host of the daily show, the cable channel has hired Marc Summers, 
former host of "Double Dare" on Nickelodeon. "Our Home" is scheduled to 
premiere June 6. 
</P>
